sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  actor C as Customer
  participant R as ROLLER
  participant P as PATCH
  participant A as Loyalty App API
  participant DB as Loyalty App Database
  participant V as Loyalty Web View

  R->>P: Booking sync updates contact loyalty field
  P->>P: Check loyalty field against cap

  alt Loyalty cap reached and no active voucher
    P->>P: Generate one-time free-pass code
    P->>P: Save contact custom fields<br/>{"loyalty_field":voucher_code,"code":"SPK-123","isActive":true}
    P->>R: POST /discounts/{discountId}/codes<br/>{"code":"SPK-123","isActive":true}
    R-->>P: 201 Created<br/>{"code":"SPK-123","isActive":true}

    alt PATCH automation delivers code
      P-->>A: POST /webhooks/patch/reward-code<br/>{"contactId":"...","email":"...","rollerCustomerId":"...","code":"SPK-123","isActive":true}
      A->>DB: Resolve customerKey<br/>{"patchContactId":"...","rollerCustomerId":"...","email":"value"}
      A->>DB: Upsert voucher by customerKey
    else Loyalty app fetches code from PATCH
      V->>A: GET /account
      A->>P: GET /v2/contacts?email={customerEmail}
      P-->>A: 200 OK<br/>{"contactId":"...","email":"...","customFields":{"loyalty_field":voucher_code,"code":"SPK-123","isActive":true,"roller_customer_id":"..."}}
      A->>DB: Resolve customerKey<br/>{"patchContactId":"...","rollerCustomerId":"...","email":"value"}
      A->>DB: Upsert voucher by customerKey
    end

    A-->>V: 200 OK<br/>{"loyalty_field":voucher_code,"code":"SPK-123","isActive":true}
    V-->>C: Show free-pass code
  end

  C->>R: Apply free-pass code at checkout
  R->>R: Validate code value and one-time status
  R-->>C: Checkout accepted (100% discount)
  R-->>A: POST /webhooks/roller/booking<br/>{"bookingId":"...","customerId":"...","email":"...","discount":{"code":"SPK-123"}}
  A->>DB: Match voucher by customerKey + voucher_code
  A->>DB: Mark voucher acquired/used by customerKey
  R->>P: Update loyalty/reward fields after redemption
  P-->>A: POST /webhooks/patch/contact-updated
